06:01.295 --> 06:02.794
It would have been nice to...

06:04.064 --> 06:06.398
Leave my land
to my kids, but...

06:08.235 --> 06:09.968
Guess god got
other plans, huh?

06:10.003 --> 06:11.002
Hey.

06:12.139 --> 06:15.273
I know how much
that place meant to you.

06:15.309 --> 06:17.976
So if there's anything
I can do to help, just...

06:18.879 --> 06:20.245
Let me know.

06:21.648 --> 06:24.149
Hey, you ready to go?

06:24.184 --> 06:25.650
Hey.

06:25.686 --> 06:27.652
Hey, uh, ralph.

06:27.688 --> 06:28.787
