-[baby laughing]

07:37.825 --> 07:40.392
-what on earth are you doing?
-[ralph angel] more milk.

07:40.427 --> 07:42.561
Baby sign language.

07:42.596 --> 07:43.695
All the books say that

07:43.730 --> 07:45.230
