12:07.928 --> 12:10.195
-Let's just be lazy.
-Mmm.

12:13.200 --> 12:14.733
-I like lazy.
-Oh, good.

12:16.937 --> 12:18.169
[chuckles]

12:20.707 --> 12:24.409
aw. God, she's changing
so fast.

12:24.444 --> 12:27.045
