huge big grin on her face.

12:33.620 --> 12:35.153
-[chuckles]
-it was so cute.

12:35.188 --> 12:37.322
All the moments I missed
with blue.

12:37.357 --> 12:39.491
[sighs] you're not missing it.

12:39.526 --> 12:41.092
You're with her every day.

12:41.928 --> 12:43.161
She'll do it again.

12:43.196 --> 12:45.029
