Now just take this.

15:11.578 --> 15:13.378
A perfectly encapsulated
moment in time

15:13.413 --> 15:16.681
illustrating the influence
of pop culture on young,
black girls.

15:16.716 --> 15:20.118
Now I'm gonna guess
this is, like... Like, 1995

15:20.153 --> 15:21.953
-when<i> waterfalls</i> came out.
-Give me that.

15:21.988 --> 15:23.855
-Oh! [laughs]
