Give it to me.

15:23.890 --> 15:26.190
[both laughing]

15:26.226 --> 15:29.727
-[nova] oh.
-You three were
crazy, sexy, cool.

15:30.597 --> 15:31.796
-I know, I'm...
-Did you just...

15:31.831 --> 15:33.298
-It sounded weird
when it came out.
-Did you really... Yeah.

15:33.333 --> 15:34.699
But you got... But look,
it's true, look.

15:35.335 --> 15:36.401
Especially left eye

15:36.436 --> 15:37.802
