the bonfire party
kind anymore, so...

26:26.419 --> 26:29.954
Well, we could maybe
do something else?

26:29.989 --> 26:32.089
-Go into town?
I know a place.
-Kenny.

26:32.124 --> 26:35.960
Look, you're really sweet,
