to stop you right here.

26:37.563 --> 26:38.829
Okay, just, uh...

26:39.899 --> 26:41.632
...Don't say no yet.

26:41.667 --> 26:43.334
It's all timing and...

26:43.936 --> 26:45.002
...I get it.

26:46.105 --> 26:48.339
I'm a patient man,
billie denton.

26:50.610 --> 26:51.775
Take it easy.

26:54.447 --> 26:56.146
[micah]<i> honestly,</i>
<i> I was just surprised</i>
<i> to see you.</i>

26:56.182 --> 26:57.481
I know.

26:57.516 --> 26:59.783
You looked like
a deer at the start
of hunting season.

26:59.819 --> 27:00.718
Oh, come on.

27:00.753 --> 27:03.220
[laughs] you never
liked surprises.

27:03.255 --> 27:05.923
Okay, to be fair, like,

27:05.958 --> 27:10.060
-surprises haven't exactly
gone over well in my family.
-Mmm.

27:10.096 --> 27:11.562
-Mmm-hmm.
-So...

27:11.597 --> 27:12.997
Yeah, and how are they?

27:13.032 --> 27:14.832
Your mom is all over the news.

27:14.867 --> 27:17.935
Yeah, I mean,
dad is killing it.

27:17.970 --> 27:20.137
You know, mom's campaign
is on fire.

27:20.172 --> 27:21.739
Yeah, squad is hot.

27:21.774 --> 27:24.174
Yeah, well, I mean,
she gotta win first.

27:24.210 --> 27:25.943
-Okay. Yeah.
-She gotta win first
but, uh...

27:26.846 --> 27:29.747
Honestly, I think
she missed california.

27:29.782 --> 27:32.182
You know what
I'm saying, like,
she loved it here, but...

27:32.218 --> 27:33.784
And you?

27:33.819 --> 27:35.519
You moving back to la too?

27:36.322 --> 27:37.354
Nah.

27:37.857 --> 27:39.590
Nah, I'm here.

27:39.625 --> 27:41.592
-Oh, so you finally free.
-[laughs]

27:41.627 --> 27:43.193
your parents miles away.

27:43.229 --> 27:44.828
-Parents miles away.
-No curfew.

27:44.864 --> 27:47.097
-No curfew.
-[laughs]

27:47.133 --> 27:48.565
-that's all.
-Nice.

27:55.374 --> 27:56.573
Walk the river with me.

27:58.144 --> 28:00.778
[groans] keke.

28:00.813 --> 28:04.615
-Micah.
-I want to, I want to,
I just, um...

28:04.650 --> 28:07.351
I got this family christening
to be to in a couple of hours.

28:07.386 --> 28:09.219
I just can't show up faded.

28:10.856 --> 28:12.523
So much for being
in the moment.

28:13.392 --> 28:14.525
But I'll see you in class.

28:15.861 --> 28:16.860
Cool?

28:20.433 --> 28:21.532
[groans softly]

28:24.403 --> 28:25.369
wait!

28:25.404 --> 28:26.403
Yo!

28:29.341 --> 28:30.674
You just gonna
leave me like that?

28:30.710 --> 28:32.810
Yeah. [laughs] catch up.

28:32.845 --> 28:34.278
[both laughing]

28:36.082 --> 28:38.916
thanks again, prosper.

28:38.951 --> 28:41.218
I want you to know
I'm happy to help
whenever you need me.

28:43.622 --> 28:44.621
Um...

28:47.893 --> 28:49.927
You know, I want you
to know that...

28:52.231 --> 28:54.098
...Sometimes I like
to get out.

28:54.800 --> 28:55.899
I mean...

28:57.136 --> 28:58.902
...With you outside...

29:00.139 --> 29:01.038
...Alone.

29:01.707 --> 29:03.207
Are you asking me out?

29:06.078 --> 29:09.747
It's, uh, it's been
a long time
since I've felt like this.

29:13.052 --> 29:15.185
Ms. Sandy,

29:15.221 --> 29:18.555
would you like to go out
with me on a real date?

29:18.591 --> 29:22.993
-Child, I was running out
of things for you to fix.
-[both laughing]

29:27.500 --> 29:30.033
[deborah on computer]
<i> nova, hey, listen.</i>

29:30.069 --> 29:32.369
<i> There's an offer on the table</i>
<i> for</i> blessings and blood.

29:32.404 --> 29:34.805
<i> They wanna turn</i>
<i> your book into a movie.</i>

29:34.840 --> 29:37.274
<i> The</i> times<i> profiles</i>
<i> have garnered a lot</i>
<i> of attention.</i>

29:37.309 --> 29:40.944
<i> The producers submitted</i>
<i>an offer and it's substantial.</i>

29:40.980 --> 29:42.780
<i> High, six figures.</i>

